The Older We Grow The Wiser We Become Or So It’s Said. But Does It Also Mean The More Vulnerable We Get? 9 Grannies In Nairobi’s Komarock Area Believe The Most Basic Of Needs Like A Meal A Day Is Increasingly Becoming A Mirage For Many Elderly Persons In Kenya, And What Some Of The Grannies In The Area Are Doing To Make That All Important Difference.